p.s:
erit $ e = d $, excessus medij 1. adde $ b - d $ erit: $ b $ medium. 

erit $ e = 3c - 2d $, excessus maximi 3. adde $ b - d $ erit: $ b + 3c - 2d $ maximum. 

if $ e = d $, the excess of the medium, add $ b - d $, then $ b $ will be the medium; 

if $ e = 3c - 2d $, the excess of the maximum, add $ b - d $, then $ b + 3c - 3d $ will be the maximum;

